title.narrative: PROCOFSERVICES and P0053 for Madhya Pradesh Power Sector Reform - Phase 2

description.narrative: This activity (PROCOFSERVICES and P0053 for Madhya Pradesh Power Sector Reform - Phase 2) is a component of Madhya Pradesh Power Sector Reform - Phase 2 reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £14,199,428. This component benefits India, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management, Public finance management (PFM), Energy policy and administrative management, Environmental policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu India LLP, PwC. The start date is 01-12-2005 and the end date is 30-06-2013.
